21Node::Node(std::unique_ptr<NodeDataModel> &&dataModel)
22 : _uid(QUuid::createUuid()), _nodeDataModel(std::move(dataModel)), _nodeState(_nodeDataModel), _nodeGeometry(_nodeDataModel),
23 _nodeGraphicsObject(nullptr)
24{
25 _nodeGeometry.recalculateSize();
26 // propagate data: model => node
27 connect(_nodeDataModel.get(), &NodeDataModel::dataUpdated, this, &Node::onDataUpdated);
28 connect(_nodeDataModel.get(), &NodeDataModel::embeddedWidgetSizeUpdated, this, &Node::onNodeSizeUpdated);
29}
30Node::~Node() = default;
31QJsonObject Node::save() const
32{
33 QJsonObject nodeJson;
34 nodeJson["id"] = _uid.toString();
35 nodeJson["model"] = _nodeDataModel->save();
36 QJsonObject obj;
37 obj["x"] = _nodeGraphicsObject->pos().x();
38 obj["y"] = _nodeGraphicsObject->pos().y();
39 nodeJson["position"] = obj;
40 return nodeJson;
41}
42void Node::restore(QJsonObject const &json)
43{
44 _uid = QUuid(json["id"].toString());
45 QJsonObject positionJson = json["position"].toObject();
46 QPointF point(positionJson["x"].toDouble(), positionJson["y"].toDouble());
47 _nodeGraphicsObject->setPos(point);
48 _nodeDataModel->restore(json["model"].toObject());
49}
50QUuid Node::id() const
51{
52 return _uid;
53}
54void Node::reactToPossibleConnection(PortType reactingPortType, std::shared_ptr<NodeDataType> reactingDataType, QPointF const &scenePoint)
55{
56 QTransform const t = _nodeGraphicsObject->sceneTransform();
57 QPointF nodePoint = t.inverted().map(scenePoint);
58 _nodeGeometry.setDraggingPosition(nodePoint);
59 _nodeGraphicsObject->update();
60 _nodeState.setReaction(NodeState::REACTING, reactingPortType, reactingDataType);
61}
62void Node::resetReactionToConnection()
63{
64 _nodeState.setReaction(NodeState::NOT_REACTING);
65 _nodeGraphicsObject->update();
66}

100void Node::propagateData(PortIndex inPortIndex) const
101{
102 NodeState const &state = nodeState();
103 NodeState::ConnectionPtrSet connections = state.connections(PortType::In, inPortIndex);
104 std::vector<std::shared_ptr<NodeData>> nodeData;
105 nodeData.reserve(connections.size());
106 for (const auto &connection : connections)
107 {
108 Connection *c = connection.second;
109 Node *outNode = c->getNode(PortType::Out);
110 PortIndex outNodeIndex = c->getPortIndex(PortType::Out);
111 std::shared_ptr<NodeData> outData = outNode->nodeDataModel()->outData(outNodeIndex);
112 TypeConverter converter = c->getTypeConverter();
113 if (converter != nullptr)
114 {
115 outData = converter(outData);
116 }
117 nodeData.push_back(outData);
118 }
119 _nodeDataModel->setInData(std::move(nodeData), inPortIndex);
120 // Recalculate the nodes visuals. A data change can result in the node taking
121 // more space than before, so this forces a recalculate+repaint on the affected
122 // node
123 _nodeGraphicsObject->setGeometryChanged();
124 _nodeGeometry.recalculateSize();
125 _nodeGraphicsObject->update();
126 _nodeGraphicsObject->moveConnections();
127}
128void Node::onDataUpdated(PortIndex index)
129{
130 auto connections = _nodeState.connections(PortType::Out, index);
131 for (auto const &c : connections) c.second->propagateData();
132}
133void Node::onNodeSizeUpdated()
134{
135 if (nodeDataModel()->embeddedWidget())
136 {
137 nodeDataModel()->embeddedWidget()->adjustSize();
138 }
139 nodeGeometry().recalculateSize();
140 for (PortType type : { PortType::In, PortType::Out })
141 {
142 for (auto &conn_set : nodeState().getEntries(type))
143 {
144 for (auto &pair : conn_set)
145 {
146 Connection *conn = pair.second;
147 conn->getConnectionGraphicsObject().move();
148 }
149 }
150 }
